	<part id="ibatis2_introduction_part">
		<title>Installation</title>
		<partintro id="ibatis2_introduction_part_partintro">
			<para>
				iBatis2 Plugin is composed of reference libraries necessary to use based on <ulink url="http://ibatis.apache.org/">iBatis2</ulink>.
			</para>
			<para role="introduction_title"><emphasis role="bold">Installation</emphasis></para>
			<para>Install ibatis2 plugin by entering the following command in the Command window.</para>
			<programlisting language="java"><![CDATA[mvn anyframe:install -Dname=ibatis2]]></programlisting>
			<para>
				The installation result can be checked by using the installed (mvn anyframe:installed) or the jetty:run (mvn clean jetty:run) commands. 
			</para>	
